name: Dinari F
description: The Dinari F dShares token (F.d) represents 1:1 ownership of shares in Ford Motor Company (NYSE: F), a leading global automobile manufacturer known for its iconic vehicles and innovative contributions to the automotive industry. Each F.d token is fully backed by a corresponding Ford stock share, securely held in a transparent and auditable treasury. By leveraging blockchain technology, F.d provides investors with exposure to Ford's equity through a regulated financial product, offering benefits such as 24/7 trading, fractional ownership, instant settlement, and enhanced liquidity.
